subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie salvaged a ragged round with a birdie-birdie finish to remain alone in fourth place after the third round of an L.P.G.A. tour sectional qualifying tournament. Her closing birdies gave her two-over 74 at Mission Hills Country Club in Rancho Mirage, Calif.
